{"tid":401230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大學生會竭盡所能阻止校方強行清拆港獨宣傳品","createTime":"2017-09-15T12:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T02:52:28.000Z","uid":28366,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cdabe75f480bfbb52cc8824290ade5a0c4729c","tid":401230,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/og73v5h6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fog73v5h6&h=e2ee6e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中大學生會會長區子灝，圖片來源：蘋果日報片段截圖</span><br />\n<br />\n中文大學校長沈祖堯下午見記者，宣佈要求中大學生會盡快移除鼓吹港獨宣傳品。中大學生會晚上召開記會會，中大學生會會長區子灝宣讀聲明，稱會竭盡所能，阻止校方強行清拆港獨宣傳品，會向校方展示不會退讓，會保護言論自由。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會批評，校長沈祖堯無心與學生商討及達成共識，而是由上而下作出命令，學生會又表示繼續有學生留守，以阻止校方強行清拆港獨宣傳品&nbsp;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/中大學生會-竭盡所能阻校方強行清拆港獨宣傳品/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E7%AB%AD%E7%9B%A1%E6%89%80%E8%83%BD%E9%98%BB%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E5%93%81%2F&d=r8wrifD8mPE8JW4%2FQmjtOtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a1ebeccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E7%AB%AD%E7%9B%A1%E6%89%80%E8%83%BD%E9%98%BB%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E5%93%81%2F&h=75ef07d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/中大學生會-竭盡所能阻校方強行清拆港獨宣傳品/</a>"},{"pid":"a6d56239a6708088c8252db6db6b3c01b882aae5","tid":401230,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e893b7176463c8a92d19b607f8b36c49cf2c021b","tid":401230,"uid":130247,"like":12,"disl